datamodel - package datamodel
 
DEFAULTCOST - Static variable in class datamodel.Delivery
The Fast Courier Services Default cost per KG shipped.
Delivery - Class in datamodel
This class represents a consignment of packages that is being or has been processed by the Fast Courier Service application.
Delivery() - Constructor for class datamodel.Delivery
Default Constructor - Builds a Delivery object with an UNKNOW consignment number for collection on the current date at the default shipping cost.

DeliveryRecord(Customer) - Constructor for class datamodel.DeliveryRecord

DeliveryStatus - Enum in datamodel
This enumeration describes the possible states that a delivery can be in as it is processed by the Fast Courier Service application
